\details{
Each study-level function is represented by its evaluations on a shared
grid of \code{G} points. The (weighted) \eqn{L^2(\mu)} inner product is
\eqn{\langle f,g\rangle = \sum_{j=1}^G w_j f(x_j) g(x_j)}, where the
