supplied, uniform weights \code{1 / G} are used.

Denoising follows Jin (2024): for each study \code{i}, let
\eqn{B_\Delta(\hat f^{(i)}) = \{j : \|\hat f^{(j)} - \hat f^{(i)}\| \le
